export const questionObj = {"Qtext": "
 
Suppose that \(p \), \(q \), \(r \), and \(s \) are in proportion. Now prove that, 
\[	
	\frac{(p - q )^3}{(q - r )^3} = \frac{p }{s } \text{ and, }
\]
\[
	\sqrt{pq } + \sqrt{qr } - \sqrt{rs } = \sqrt{(p + q - r )(q + r - s )}
\]
\newline

", "Steps": [{"id": "s1", "n_params": 0, "step_txt": "$$\text{
 
It is given that $p $, $q $, $r $, and $s $ are in proportion.}$$
\[
	\Rightarrow \frac{p }{q } = \frac{q }{r } = \frac{r }{s } = t \textrm{ (assume)}
\]
\[
	\Rightarrow r = ts 
\]"}, {"id": "s2", "n_params": 0, "step_txt": "
\[
	\Rightarrow q = tr = t ^2 s 
\]
\[
	\Rightarrow p = tq = t ^3 s 
\]"}]} 

 export const resp = [{"data": [], "text": " "}, {"data": [], "text": " "}]
